.TH "STX SWEEP" "1" "2026-04-20" "0.2.0" "stx sweep Manual"
.SH NAME
stx\-sweep \- Run loss sweep (mse, listnet, approx_ndcg)...
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stx sweep
[OPTIONS]
.SH DESCRIPTION
Run loss sweep (mse, listnet, approx_ndcg) and merge summaries.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-c,\fP \-\-config FILE
Universe experiment YAML.  [default: configs/universe.yaml]
.TP
\fB\-\-synthetic\fP
Use synthetic universe data.
.TP
\fB\-o,\fP \-\-output\-format [text|json]
text: comparison table; json: merged sweep summary.  [default: text]
